      {
        "content": "Mishandled exception: send() failure ignored\n\nContract uses payee.send(amount) and ignores the returned bool. If the payee is a contract that reverts on receive, the send silently fails while state marks the payment complete. Fix: check the return value and revert, or use a withdrawal pattern.",
